  <!-- CLOSING REFLECTION - Left-Aligned Bounded -->
  <section class="expertise-hero">
    <div class="expertise-hero__image">
      <Image src={heroPhinisi} alt="The Banggai Islands at dawn" />
    </div>
    <div class="expertise-hero__overlay"></div>
    <div class="expertise-hero__inner">
      <div class="expertise-hero__content">
        <span class="expertise-hero__label">Go Gently</span>
        <h2 class="expertise-hero__title">A Fragile Transition</h2>
        <p class="expertise-hero__text">
          On our last morning, we went back to Paisupok Lake one more time. We
          didn't take photos. We just drifted in the canoe, listening to the
          hornbills in the canopy.
        </p>
        <p class="expertise-hero__text">
          The Banggai Islands are in a fragile transition. The road to Luk
          Panenteng is being widened. More homestays are being built. A "resort"
          is rumored. In five years, the silence we experienced might be gone,
          replaced by the hum of constant generators and tour buses.
        </p>
        <p class="expertise-hero__text">
          Right now, it is a destination that demands something from
          you-patience, resilience, and a willingness to be uncomfortable. In
          exchange, it offers glimpses of a world that feels untouched, even if
          the edges are starting to fray. If you go, go gently. Tread lightly on
          the boardwalks, take your trash with you, and appreciate the dark,
          quiet nights where the only light comes from the stars and the erratic
          glow of fireflies. It is imperfect, difficult, and absolutely worth
          the journey.
        </p>
        <div class="expertise-hero__stats">
          <div>
            <div class="expertise-hero__stat-value">Sept-Nov</div>
            <div class="expertise-hero__stat-label">Ideal Season</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="expertise-hero__stat-value">Cash</div>
            <div class="expertise-hero__stat-label">Essential</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="expertise-hero__stat-value">Patience</div>
            <div class="expertise-hero__stat-label">Required</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

