  <section id="biodiversity" class="section section--cream">
    <div class="section__inner">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-header__label">Wildlife & Nature</span>
        <h2 class="section-header__title">What You'll See</h2>
        <p class="section-header__subtitle">
          From the endemic Banggai Cardinalfish to stingless jellyfish, sea
          turtles, and the mirror-like waters of Paisupok-here's what defines
          the Banggai experience.
