        <div class="bio-card">
          <div class="bio-card__image">
            <Image src={mantaRays} alt="Banggai Cardinalfish" />
          </div>
          <div class="bio-card__content">
            <h3 class="bio-card__name">Banggai Cardinalfish</h3>
            <p class="bio-card__latin">Pterapogon kauderni</p>
            <p class="bio-card__desc">
              Striking black-and-white fish endemic to this tiny region.
              Aquarium trade nearly wiped them out; they are recovering. See
              them under the main jetty in Banggai Town, hovering among sea
              urchins.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bio-card">
          <div class="bio-card__image">
            <Image src={caveDiving} alt="Stingless jellyfish" />
          </div>
          <div class="bio-card__content">
            <h3 class="bio-card__name">Stingless Jellyfish</h3>
            <p class="bio-card__latin">Paisubatango Lagoon</p>
            <p class="bio-card__desc">
              Thousands pulsating in the brackish green gloom of Paisubatango.
              Smaller and murkier than Raja Ampat's or Kakaban's-eerie and
              beautiful. No sunscreen or repellent; chemicals kill them.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bio-card">
          <div class="bio-card__image">
            <Image src={softCoralMangrove} alt="Lake Paisupok" />
          </div>
          <div class="bio-card__content">
            <h3 class="bio-card__name">Lake Paisupok</h3>
            <p class="bio-card__latin">The mirror lake</p>
            <p class="bio-card__desc">
              Freshwater connected to the sea via underground tunnels-no waves,
              dead silent. Deep turquoise; visibility to every submerged log and
              rock. Like floating on glass.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bio-card">
          <div class="bio-card__image">
            <Image src={coralReef} alt="Reefs Bone Baru" />
          </div>
          <div class="bio-card__content">
            <h3 class="bio-card__name">Table Corals & Reefs</h3>
            <p class="bio-card__latin">Bone Baru, Mandel</p>
            <p class="bio-card__desc">
              Island-hopping reveals vibrant coral just offshore-massive table
              corals and healthy soft corals. Bone Baru has incredibly fine
              white sand and thriving reef.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bio-card">
          <div class="bio-card__image">
            <Image src={wayagAerial} alt="Jungle and coast" />
          </div>
          <div class="bio-card__content">
            <h3 class="bio-card__name">Jungle & Coast</h3>
            <p class="bio-card__latin">Peleng</p>
            <p class="bio-card__desc">
              Dense coconut plantations, overhanging jungle at the lake, small
              fishing hamlets along the coast. Hornbills in the canopy;
              fireflies and stars at night.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bio-card">
          <div class="bio-card__image">
            <Image src={misoolLagoon} alt="Sea turtles" />
          </div>
          <div class="bio-card__content">
            <h3 class="bio-card__name">Sea Turtles</h3>
            <p class="bio-card__latin">Mandel & reefs</p>
            <p class="bio-card__desc">
              Possible on island-hopping days-e.g. Mandel. Currents can be
              strong; choose calm spots for snorkelling.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bio-card">
          <div class="bio-card__image">
            <Image src={karstTurquoise} alt="King's Bath" />
          </div>
          <div class="bio-card__content">
            <h3 class="bio-card__name">The King's Bath</h3>
            <p class="bio-card__latin">Pemandian Raja</p>
            <p class="bio-card__desc">
              Freshwater spring historically reserved for Banggai royalty. Cool,
              clear water; now a public swimming hole. Concrete surroundings;
              local hangout.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bio-card">
          <div class="bio-card__image">
            <Image src={beachTurquoise} alt="Fireflies and stars" />
